Games::Sequential version 0.11
==============================

Games::Sequential provides an object oriented framework for
developing sequential games. It pretty much only has support for
keeping history (thus allowing undo) at the moment, though more
is planned.

This is the initial release.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module will carp or croak rather than warn and die.

